WEBVTT

00:03:59.110 --> 00:04:03.656
And then, over time, they might look
to the patterns of their wins and losses,

00:04:03.656 --> 00:04:07.243
to glean even more meaningful
conclusions and insights.

00:04:08.661 --> 00:04:11.998
The same process can and should
be used in the workplace,

00:04:11.998 --> 00:04:15.543
and I don't think we need to watch
video replays of our meetings

00:04:15.543 --> 00:04:17.128
to dissect what took place.

00:04:17.169 --> 00:04:18.296
(Laughter)

00:04:18.337 --> 00:04:21.132
I don't know about you,
but that might feel kind of creepy.

00:04:21.173 --> 00:04:22.174
(Laughter)

00:04:23.134 --> 00:04:26.971
Reflection can be done
through a variety of different formats:

00:04:27.013 --> 00:04:28.764
purposeful thinking,

00:04:28.764 --> 00:04:32.601
written journal entries,
audio notes, pitches,